⍝ TakeAxis.tc
⍝ ═══════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ Precond: A simple scalar/vector integer; X∊⍳⍴⍴B; implicit ⎕IO
      ⍝ inv: (⍴Z)[,X] ←→ |,A
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ ⍴⍴B
      B ← ⎕RVAL 2 (5 6) (,0 1 0 0 0)
      A ← 3                                   ⍝ take 3 along axis 1
      X ← 1
      Z ← A↑[X]B
      ((⍴Z)[X]) ≡ |,A
1
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ ⍴⍴B
1
      ⍝ inv: A↑[X]B ←→ ⊃[X](⊂A)↑¨⊂[X]B
      (A↑[X]B) ≡ ⊃[X](⊂A)↑¨⊂[X]B
1
